links.title: Aerojet Rocketdyne soars 26% after Lockheed Martin announces $4.4 billion acquisition of the rocket engine manufacturer
links.description: Shares of Aerojet Rocketdyne gained as much as 26% to $53.10 on Monday after defense giant Lockheed Martin announced its acquiring the company in a $4.4 billion deal. Aerojet manufactures defense rocket engines and will give Lockheed a larger stake in the increasingly competitive space and hypersonic technology space.
